 render him useful... he has a pet.  If he goes LD he loses money... we know why.  However, you guys know better than me, if there's some reason I shouldn't bother chasing the dream of being a living GOD (what I view a high lvl wizard as) please let me know and I'll put my stuff on a chanter or a mage... actually, I can never be a pet caster again, to heck with it, I'm gonna follow through on this one... oh to be the guy PULLED TO instead of the guy running amongst the mobs, possibly getting lost/gakked on his way back to the group.<br>
<br>
I am interested in knowing why I should regret getting excited as my future as a wizard, please respond.<br>
<br>
Sincerely yours:<br>
<br>
Vendricus:<br>
